{"id":232249811,"title":"摔破玻璃吸管 求幫選新吸管QAQ","content":"大一開始就有在使用環保吸管\n最初是用不鏽鋼吸管\n後來看到不鏽鋼吸管很髒的新聞就不敢用了😓\n\n最近買的玻璃吸管被我弟摔破（小五）\n而且已經是第三支... ==\n\n想說這樣也蠻危險的\n乾脆順勢換成矽膠吸管\n（我不太喜歡塑膠吸管的口感）\n\n除了蠻有名的 Dr.si 之外\n看到嘖嘖最近有出一個 Air 空氣吸管\nhttps://www.zeczec.com/projects/airstraw\n\n前陣子也有看到版友在討論\n樣式蠻好看的 而且看起來很好咬哈哈\n\n我打算買藍色的\n不知道有買的大家是買哪個款式？\n\n被這張圖燒到🔥\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/2Gek2dh.jpg","excerpt":"大一開始就有在使用環保吸管，最初是用不鏽鋼吸管，後來看到不鏽鋼吸管很髒的新聞就不敢用了，最近買的玻璃吸管被我弟摔破（小五），而且已經是第三支... ==，想說這樣也蠻危險的，乾脆順勢換成矽膠吸管，（我","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"49eed176-a7ad-492c-b6cf-77733ab633ef","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-10-07T10:43:34.852Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-07T10:43:34.852Z","commentCount":23,"likeCount":27,"tags":[],"topics":["吸管","環保","環保吸管","選色"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"無痕生活","forumAlias":"ecolife","school":"國立臺灣師範大學","department":"國文學系","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":true,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":27}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/2Gek2dh.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"ce41f692-b986-4668-acea-0a9a6ec95d74","url":"https://i.imgur.com/2Gek2dhl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/2Gek2dhl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/2Gek2dhl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-10-07T10:43:34.852Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-07T10:43:34.852Z"},{"id":"ce41f692-b986-4668-acea-0a9a6ec95d74","url":"http://i.imgur.com/2Gek2dh.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/2Gek2dh","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/2Gek2dhl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-10-07T10:43:34.852Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-07T10:43:34.852Z"}],"postAvatar":""}